# four constant polygons

Display "octagon_lighted.tiff" "file" "rgb"

Format 320 320 1
Projection "perspective" "fov" 90

WorldBegin

LightSource "pointlight" 1 "intensity" 10 "from" [0.5 1.0 0.0]

Surface "plastic"

Polygon "P" [ 0  0  2    0  1  3    1  0  3]
Polygon "P" [ 0  0  2    1  0  3    0 -1  3]
Polygon "P" [ 0  0  2    0 -1  3   -1  0  3]
Polygon "P" [ 0  0  2   -1  0  3    0  1  3]

WorldEnd
